{"name": "/app.bitbag/en-US/phoneScreenshots/08.png", "sha256": "008bc32230d01e043b90736d3d2a32fce898a309130185d85118be72aee92166", "size": 260841}, {"name": "/app.bitbag/en-US/phoneScreenshots/09.png", "sha256": "6980c8a7bc42917de96080ae94660e84ad5ae4177aac9c8a2a74fdb1cc42db4e", "size": 216014}]}}, "name": {"en-US": "Bag"}, "summary": {"en-US": "Bitcoin portfolio & net worth. No ads, no accounts."}, "description": {"en-US": "Track your Bitcoin net worth in real time. Enter your BTC holdings, pick up to 3 fiat currencies, and watch your portfolio value update alongside live price charts and a DCA tracker.\n\nBitcoin-only. No altcoins. No ads. No accounts. No analytics. Your holdings never leave your device.\n\nFEATURES\n\n* Net worth in up to 3 fiat currencies (USD, EUR, GBP and 50+ more)\n* Live BTC price charts - 1D / 1W / 1M / 1Y / ALL-time\n* DCA tracker with cost basis and P&L\n* Home screen widget with live price and net worth\n* Mempool fee estimates (sat/vB)\n* Sats / BTC display toggle\n* Dark and light theme\n\nPRO - one-time purchase, no subscription\n\n* Watch-only zpub wallet tracking (BIP84 / P2WPKH)\n* Tor routing via Orbot for full network privacy\n* Custom Esplora server support\n* Bitcoin Health Check - privacy score across all wallets\n* Sentinel: always-on balance monitoring with mempool alerts\n* Mempool fee alerts (above/below threshold)\n\nPRIVACY & SECURITY\n\nOnly address hashes ever reach the explorer - your zpub and balance stay on-device. All network paths can be routed through Tor (Orbot required). No phone-home, no telemetry, no third-party SDKs.\n\nOpen source: github.com/UXAVIA/bag"}, "icon": {"en-US": {"name": "/app.bitbag/en-US/icon_ADSYpODhuowSipQIf0aTOWkuWY7PBhv-9G3UPg5ICBs=.png", "sha256": "003498a4e0e1ba8c128a94087f469339692e598ecf061bfef46dd43e0e48081b", "size": 17587}}, "preferredSigner": "2969bf3df9a1058556af8f7f74a4c75a5632f323a0508533468c4c6cf4bf140a"}, "versions": {"c2c72aed41d96543bed3f7a2af059e1c8ba9e3f183726e9ceced521e0